{"tid":980223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"200磅胖漢飛墮簷篷　困兩粒鐘獲救惜不治","createTime":"2019-01-13T10:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T12:23:11.000Z","uid":160807,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a01c8de5c02e5d58a9dd45e899eca327e25606db","tid":980223,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190113/photo/bkn-20190113011023845-0113_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190113114934\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190113011023845-0113_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190113114934&h=210e4756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190113/photo/bkn-20190113011023845-0113_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190113114934\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190113011023845-0113_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190113114934&h=7910ee7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名體重約200磅姓杜(33歲)胖漢，今日(13日)凌晨零時許，在新蒲崗崇齡街63至89號崇齡大廈墮樓，昏迷倒臥4樓一單位的石棉瓦簷篷上，姓曾(52歲)女戶主見狀報警求助，與此同時，事主的哥哥亦發現其弟不知所終，經一番尋找始獲悉事件。<br />\n<br />\n消防員接報到場架起升降台施救，惟因簷篷受損，不排除會有坍塌危險，故需做足安全措施，始能展開救援工作，拯救近2小時才能將杜救下，他滿臉鮮血已陷昏迷，救護員即場為他進行急救後，並由一名男親友陪同送院，惟送抵醫院搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警員經調查後，證實墮樓男事主與哥哥及其他家人同為上址住客，並於一單位墮下。杜本身有工作，現場無檢獲遺書，墮樓原因有待調查。受事件影響，上址快線一度封閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190113/bkn-20190113011023845-0113_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190113%2Fbkn-20190113011023845-0113_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=O0Ck5FDcW8taR8KUalswuqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=40986055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190113/bkn-20190113011023845-0113_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"f0c716008c207111108059cf6c7b5caf7646fd42","tid":980223,"uid":207734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3072b1645b755054d13c8f70519374ab0c9a57d5","tid":980223,"uid":5490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"成個空投炸彈咁重"},{"pid":"55f08fdff62e90a7aef398ad1472cc8eb47faab6","tid":980223,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c716008c207111108059cf6c7b5caf7646fd42","tid":980223,"uid":207734,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T11:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要睇埋身高先知, 你有米9,200磅可以望落都唔見"},{"pid":"9e1446fe183ea7a5fc2690f5167ad3c786802023","tid":980223,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"唔肥*"},{"pid":"86e8956c2e2b39ca2877089657398e45ad5fe322","tid":980223,"uid":64847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"肥人好難同佢做CPR"},{"pid":"9e1be916a4e79f8e371135398721c7d154903a61","tid":980223,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"又死一個肥人，好事嚟"}]}